description:
&lt;p&gt;If you relish a challenge, are caring and compassionate and have a passion to help others or simply fancy a fresh start, then we need people who share our values and vision to join us as Mental Health Practitioners in our Wirral Complex Needs Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will provide a specialist service to clients with personality disorder and complex trauma, undertaking assessment and consultation with complex, personality disordered clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will take professional responsibility and exercise autonomous judgement with regard to professional practice; agree and manage time-limited interventions in accordance with specific service level agreements/service policies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have demonstrable post registration experience and have the ability to assess risk, be able to provide advice and consultation on client care utilising excellent interpersonal skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return we will provide the necessary support, training and supervision to ensure your development within your role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Todd Jones Team Manager Email address toddjones@nhs.net Telephone number 0151 488 8156&lt;/p&gt;
